                  </persName>
            . I was clerk to Sir Peter Pole and Co. for many years. There was one Edward Smith kept cash there, but he died eight or nine years ago; we had no other customer of that name.</p>
               <p>Cross-examined by MR. PHILLIPS. Q. Are your books here? A. No. I speak from my knowledge; the books are at the Bankrupt-office.</p>
